            "text": "<p>Refunds will be issued to the original method of payment, or store credit. We cannot process a return if no purchasing information is available. <strong>Please note</strong>: <strong>Shipping costs are not refundable on returns.  </strong></p><p>Once we receive your return, your refund will be issued within 5 to 10 business days. Your bank or credit card institution may take up to 2 weeks to acknowledge the credit after we process the refund. </p><p>We cannot refund a purchase made with store credit to another method of payment. Gift cards are non-transferable, non-refundable and are not redeemable for cash. We cannot replace lost or stolen gift cards. </p><p>We do not offer free returns for international orders. Customers are responsible for covering the cost of any returned items. </p>",
